text: Gilching-Argelsried station is a railway station in the municipality of Gilching, located in the Starnberg district in Upper Bavaria, Germany. ==References== ==External links== Category:Munich S-Bahn stations Category:Railway stations in Bavaria Category:Buildings and structures in Starnberg (district) Category:Railway stations in Germany opened in 1903 Category:1903 establishments in Bavaria
